1. Open the default web browser
2. Go to www.dominos.com
3. Enter your address information
4. Hit Continue
5. Choose Cheese
6. Choose Hand-Tossed
7. Choose regular sauce
8. Add to cart
9. Don't choose any extra options that pop-up
10. Continue to check out
11. Enter the credit card info
12. Check out
13. Await pizza
14. Wait more
15. Get upset that pizza hasn't arrived yet
16. Answer the door
17. Claim your pizza